rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I used to think this was a fine place
to live as long as you're used to it...

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0002
rows.name:
But then I found out the anti-imperial
organization Brionac had a hideout
right below here!

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, no wonder the Superbians
aren't keen on this area with a nasty
lot like them hanging around...

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I didn't know much about Brionac
up until just recently...

rows.label: tlk41700151_02_msg0005
rows.name:
But I guess if I'm going to live here in
Superbia, I should be more sensitive
to those kinds of issues.
